name: Humpback whale capsizes boat
summary: On August 21st, 2022, a humpback whale breached and landed on a boat off the coast of New Hampshire, causing the vessel to capsize and throwing two men overboard. Witnesses reported that the whale appeared to be agitated and may have been targeting the boat due to fishing activity. The two men were rescued by the Coast Guard and taken to a nearby hospital for treatment of non-life-threatening injuries. The incident was captured on video and widely shared on social media, sparking interest and discussion about the potential reasons for the whale's behavior.

name: Nepal plane crash
summary: A tragic plane crash has claimed the lives of 18 individuals in Nepal's capital. The aircraft went down shortly after takeoff from Kathmandu's Tribhuvan International Airport. The pilot is the lone survivor of the incident. Aviation authorities have confirmed the fatalities, including 16 Nepali nationals, 2 Indians, and 1 Irish citizen. The cause of the crash is still under investigation, as search and rescue operations continue at the site. Witnesses and officials reported that the plane appeared to lose control and plummeted to the ground, bursting into flames. The incident has sent shockwaves through the nation and the aviation community, prompting an outpouring of condolences and support for the victims' families.
